{"id": 2633, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常中，你都有哪些答案依赖症？", "description": "究竟怎样才能完美地开椰子？", "record_count": 4092, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181119172215A9xGrXz7P8BLKSl4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-20T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 314880, "content": "玩游戏先看攻略", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523374}, {"id": 314118, "content": "咖啡咖啡咖啡！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519313}, {"id": 312329, "content": "每次网购东西，每当结账时都想要在便宜一点哪怕无足轻重的五块钱都特别开心，可是退货的时候对快递费缺一点也不觉得贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354303}, {"id": 314121, "content": "看完一部电影上知乎看影评", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821543}, {"id": 333066, "content": "电影书 购物之类的评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605759}, {"id": 312076, "content": "面向百度编程", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244502}, {"id": 312338, "content": "基本靠百度过日子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510491}, {"id": 315677, "content": "当然是手机，任何东西找不见了都想用手机拨个电话看看在哪里", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527871}, {"id": 312606, "content": "看电影先去豆瓣看导演、编剧、制片人是谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507908}, {"id": 312103, "content": "玩rpg看最佳对话攻略", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391402}, {"id": 315433, "content": "买口红看试色", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525990}, {"id": 312107, "content": "遇难事必百度", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999390}, {"id": 312621, "content": "看剧看电影一定要看剧透，正在更新的剧如果有小说IP就看几集之后看小说结局，都没有就找别人的推测分析，完结的剧看一两集就看最后一集结局，结局不好就会弃剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511816}, {"id": 312379, "content": "一定会称体重每天，虽然变化不大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479429}, {"id": 312383, "content": "百度，知乎，小红书等软件成了日常第一反应……总觉得思考没有搜索来得快，丢失了很多思考的能力……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505362}, {"id": 312640, "content": "依赖数据逆推分析，不然干活没底气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511409}, {"id": 313415, "content": "买书/借书先看出版社", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1516472}, {"id": 312136, "content": "看看知乎，看看百度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277866}, {"id": 311884, "content": "看书看电影先去豆瓣看看评分怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 956, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684014}, {"id": 311885, "content": "打游戏寻找完美攻略", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832055}, {"id": 311888, "content": "买大件儿或其他不了解的东西必上知乎搜相关问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 562, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508581}, {"id": 311889, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 555522}, {"id": 311890, "content": "别人问我的问题会追求准确回答，不知道立马百度，不能瞎说", "image": null, "praise_count": 467, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 318035, "content": "看电影先看影评", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471964}, {"id": 311893, "content": "买任何吃的东西都要先看热量表，虽然看了也阻止不了我买它。", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508586}, {"id": 311895, "content": "选那个能让我最开心的答案。", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755649}, {"id": 311896, "content": "看书要先查那个译本最好", "image": null, "praise_count": 286, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320075}, {"id": 311897, "content": "想要了解国外的体育明星、娱乐明星时依赖维基百科", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2362}, {"id": 311898, "content": "写作业查字典", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424243}, {"id": 311899, "content": "做任何事先上知乎", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247355}, {"id": 311900, "content": "刷慕课的时候\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467661}, {"id": 314204, "content": "买东西前先上知乎搜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295432}, {"id": 311901, "content": "听医生的话吃药", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696088}, {"id": 311902, "content": "做作业先找答案 虽然想自己做", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431466}, {"id": 311903, "content": "好像没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 311904, "content": "都是家里没矿给逼的", "image": null, "praise_count": 150, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455065}, {"id": 312160, "content": "听网易云一定要翻评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305631}, {"id": 311906, "content": "每次买什么必须要知乎、豆瓣、b站看一遍测评", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1130030}, {"id": 311907, "content": "先看看别人说的什么，再答这道题", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932116}, {"id": 311908, "content": "写作业的时候 先在草稿纸上算一遍 答案对了再往作业纸上写", "image": null, "praise_count": 215, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418449}, {"id": 311909, "content": "买淘宝看评价\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 594, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507888}, {"id": 311910, "content": "高数", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483109}, {"id": 312422, "content": "做什么之前都看评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510781}, {"id": 311911, "content": "不亲眼看别人用过。不敢买的电子产品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 315496, "content": "看电影先看影评再决定买不买票", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 311913, "content": "写作业的时候，打开小袁搜题，作业帮", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508662}, {"id": 314217, "content": "看东西时，看评论，可能会跟风评论:-D", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514320}, {"id": 311914, "content": "在床上必须完美的进出200下，不能多不能少", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143591}, {"id": 311915, "content": "文综主观题日常", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485893}, {"id": 311917, "content": "被同学怀疑乘法运算，自己拿计算机重新算了一遍，模糊不懂的英语单词，一定会再去百度有道翻译一遍！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}]}